data.description: Amazing location, proximity to all of your shopping needs and easy access to the freeway. Very well cared for home in a beautifully mature neighborhood. Meticulously maintained!! New HVAC, roof, paint, flooring, and counters. Enjoy the large yard, and RV parking. This home also has an ADU, perfect for guests or additional income. Owner has been successful renting this ADU out for $1000 a month.
